name: Goose Battle Royale
description:
This game was developed in a week for Rutgers Club Creation of Games Society in spring of 2019. 

You play as a goose among a set of 99 others. The ultimate goal - WIN. With you're two rudimentary abilities, a peck and a honk (Left mouse/Right mouse). Ride the Rutgers bus into the field of Busch Campus and win them all!
